{
  "name": "Alchemist",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/fleur-de-lis-yellow.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Skill</p><p>You have studied the secrets of alchemy and are an expert in its practice, gaining the following benefits:</p><p>• Increase your Intelligence score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• You gain proficiency with the Alchemist Kit.</p><p>If you are already proficient, you instead gain Mastery.</p><p>• As an action, you can identify any one poison or consumable liquid within 5 feet of you, as if you had tasted it.</p><p>You must see it for this benefit to work.</p><p>• Over the course of any short rest, you can create one set of Assassins Blood.</p><p>You must have an Alchemist Kit with at least one charge with you when you do.</p><p>• Over the course of any short rest, you can temporarily improve the potency of one poison, chakra or blood pill.</p><p>To use this benefit, you must spend the charge of the Alchemist kit.</p><p>When you do, you enhance the following; </p><p>- Potency of a Poison – Increase its save DC by +2 and damage by one additional damage die.</p><p>- Potency of a Chakra Pill – Increase the chakra gained by 1 die.</p><p>- Potency of a Blood Pill – Increase the hit points gained by 2 dice.</p><p></p>",
